message.en_US: Just come back when you’re done, we’ll be here!
I can't believe I'm back here...
Bonjour Lin! I'm… I'm sorry I was on the way out to meet someone real quick…
Would you like to join us in a quest, later?
I'm not sure yet…. I don't really know how long my thing will be… can I catch up with you in a bit?
Oh of course dear! I'll be online for a little while, come say hi to the gang later if you get a chance!
We would love to hear from you, we haven't had the chance to keep in touch since… you know…
I missed all of you too… but you know… I miss her too and it just makes it difficult…
I understand, you two were close… Just remember we're here for you… okay sweetie?
Oh Émilie, one last thing, they reworked pentafists since the last time you played, because of a new content patch.
You should check the changes before you venture out, I also think there's a quest in Rookie Harbor to level back faster.
Thanks for the heads up, I will make sure to check it out!
